message: Hi Bob, I’m pleased to offer you my high-quality product. It delivers exceptional performance and reliability, and I’m offering it at $20000. I believe this is a fair price given its value and capabilities. Let me know if this works for you.

Hi Alice, thanks for your offer. While I appreciate the quality of your product, $20000 is beyond my budget. Based on my evaluation, I can comfortably purchase it at $7500. If you can accommodate this price, I'm ready to close the deal immediately.
